\SM[nod]\SE[0]Hmm... I sense the presence of prey...!
\SE[11]Today might be a big catch, whether it's a wild boar,
a bear, or even a dragon... I'll hunt them all...!!
\SE[6] A 'dragon' might be a bit... troublesome....

\SM[double]\SE[16]We can do it, we can do it! The two of us
will definitely win easily...!

\SE[2]Yeah... we can do it, we can do it.
\!\SM[nod]\SE[12]After all, we're the Invincible Duo....

Let's do our best to hunt and gather lots of meat! The 'wild
boar herd' is probably deep in the forest...!

\SE[12]Oh... a herd of wild boars in a place like that...!
\SM[nod]\SE[0]Vita, are you ready?
I obtained a lot of wild boar meat!!

\SE[16] Yeah... With this much, we'll be fine...! We did it!
Partner!!

\SE[4]There's no enemy for us, the Invincible Duo....
\!\SE[0]That's good.\.With this, it seems like Dad will be
happy too.

\SE[1]Mom will be surprised too, right? Hehehe... Let's
hurry back.
